Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,CHIEF CHIEF CHIEF
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,获胜者 NOMAD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,让这一切结束吧 冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,世事难遂人愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么货真价实的拳击手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个打假拳的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像无法接受 但那一拳确实很扎实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脑子都颤抖了 像小鹿似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你那时候刻意闪开 没有造成致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那样怎么可能造成伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,客人都看得很开心 这不就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是职业拳击手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明明上过真正的擂台 你不为现在的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,感到羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那你又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是因为你沉溺于这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,躺在那的 就应该是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,多保重 NOMAD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么把我带到这种鬼地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那还不是得看你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么上头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自暴自弃 连命都不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,却还保留着这份渺小的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,自那之后 已经过了5年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,直到看见光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,ROUND 1 亡灵吟唱安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他的心早已死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,像迷失于荒野的行尸走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找死之归所的不羁亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:23:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,蜂鸟对伫立的旅人歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是深爱的故乡之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,过去与未来 早已舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,无处可去 也不曾有方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,lalala lala lalala lala
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,歌声停息 蜂鸟飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,lalala lala lalala lala
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,旅人心中 亮起微弱的灯火
